---
layout: base.njk
---
<h1 class="visually-hidden">AISlopWatch — AI slop and hype, screenshotted, labeled, and blamed</h1>
<section class="intro prose">
  <p>
    <strong>AI is fine. What people do with it often isn't.</strong> Two kinds of
    cringe, screenshotted: <strong>slop</strong> — low-effort machine filler nobody
    bothered to read back — and <strong>hype</strong> — humans swearing a chatbot
    loves them and made them rich. We name names. <a href="{{ '/about/' | url }}">More →</a>
  </p>
</section>

<section class="legend" aria-label="What the verdicts mean">
  <span class="legend-label mono">the two crimes</span>
  <ul class="legend-list">
    {%- for key, cat in categories %}{% if key == "slop" or key == "hype" %}
    <li>
      <a class="badge badge-stamp" data-cat="{{ key }}" href="{{ ('/tags/' ~ key ~ '/') | url }}">{{ cat.label }}</a>
      <span class="legend-blurb">{{ cat.blurb }}</span>
    </li>
    {%- endif %}{% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

{% set board = collections.posts | rankByEngagement(engagement) %}
{%- if board.length %}
<section class="shame">
  <div class="shame-head mono">
    <span>// hall of shame</span>
    <a href="{{ '/trending/' | url }}">full board →</a>
  </div>
  <ol class="shame-list" data-board>
    {%- for row in board %}{% if loop.index <= 3 %}
    <li class="shame-item" data-slug="{{ row.post.fileSlug }}">
      <a class="shame-link" href="{{ row.post.url | url }}">
        <span class="shame-rank mono">{{ loop.index }}</span>
        <span class="shame-title">{{ row.post.data.title }}</span>
        <span class="shame-score mono">🔨 <span class="live-votes">{{ row.up }}</span> · 👁 <span class="live-views">0</span></span>
      </a>
    </li>
    {%- endif %}{% endfor %}
  </ol>
</section>
{%- endif %}

{%- if collections.posts.length %}
{% include "taglist.njk" %}

<div class="sortbar mono" data-sort hidden>
  <span class="sortbar-label">sort</span>
  <button type="button" data-sort-by="newest" class="is-active" aria-pressed="true">newest</button>
  <button type="button" data-sort-by="blamed" aria-pressed="false">most blamed</button>
  <button type="button" data-sort-by="viewed" aria-pressed="false">most viewed</button>
</div>

{% set postlist = collections.posts | reverse %}
{% include "postlist.njk" %}
{%- else %}
<p class="prose empty-state">
  No sightings logged yet. The internet is extruding slop as you read this —
  <a href="https://github.com/{{ site.repo }}/issues" rel="noopener">bring the first receipts →</a>
</p>
{%- endif %}
